-6814-600x374.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"4\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\">\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                                <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Spike prime</b></h5>\n                                <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-1\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">Creating Your Brand</h6>\n                                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Újabb LEGO robotikai rendszer, amely a Mindstorms-t váltotta oktatási célokra. Saját hubbal, motorokkal és érzékelőkkel, programozható grafikus blokkokkal és Python-nal. Jó átmenet kezdőknek és haladóknak is.<br></p>\n                            </div>\n                            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"page5.html\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-black\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">További információ</a></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div><div class=\"embla__slide slider-image item\" mbr-style=\"{'margin-left': gap + 'rem', 'margin-right': gap + 'rem'}\">\n                        <div class=\"slide-content\">\n                            <div class=\"item-img\">\n                                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/xgo-v2-ai-dog-robot-with-15-dofs-w-arm-for-microbit-without-micro-bit-board-elecfreaks-ef08289-474x474.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" tit