\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                    <b>Technikai jellemzők</b></h4>\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                    List main features of your project in this block\n                </h5>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-3 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-left\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText || showLink\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\"><b>Programmable Hub</b><br><b><br></b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .link\">Központi egység 5×5 LED mátrix-szel a visszajelzéshez.<br><br>6 I/O port: motorok és szenzorok csatlakoztatására.<br><br>6 tengelyes giroszkóp és gyorsulásmérő a pontos mozgáskövetéshez.<br><br>Bluetooth és USB-C kapcsolódás.</p>\n                        <div class=\"link-wrap\">\n                            <h6 class=\"link mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showLink\" data-app-selector=\".link\">\n                                <a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"#\">Learn more &gt;</a>\n                            </h6>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-3 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-left\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText || showLink\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Motorok</b><br><b><br></b>\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .link\">2 közepes motor: precíziós, lassabb mechanikai mozgásokhoz.<br><br>1 nagy motor: erősebb, nagyobb terhelésű mechanizmusokhoz.<br><br>Beépített forgásérzékelő minden motorban.</p>\n                        <div class=\"link-wrap\">\n                            <h6 class=\"link mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showLink\" data-app-selector=\".link\">\n                                <a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"#\">Learn more &gt;</a>\n                            </h6>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-3 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper mb-4\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box align-left\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText || showLink\">\n                        <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\">\n                            <b>Programozás és bővíthetőség</b></h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .link\"><br>LEGO SPIKE alkalmazás: Scratch-szerű vizuális blokkok, Python támogatás.<br>Szenzorok, motorok és LED mátrix vezérlése.<br><br>Python API segítségével komplex logikák, harmadik féltől származó érzékelők csatlakoztatása.<br></p>\n                        <div class=\"link-wrap\">\n                            <h6 class=\"link mbr-fonts-style align-left\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showLink\" data-app-selector=\".link\">\n                                <a class=\"text-primary\" href=\"#\">Learn more &gt;</a>\n                            </h6>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
